ot"><p>RCA-scale = Road Condition Information (0 - 50 m) in front of a moving car based on data from a laser sensor and a world first data processing technique.</p></div></div></div></div></section><!-- Contact information --><section class="contact container-fluid"><div class="row-fluid contact"><div class="contact_container col-xs-12"><div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 contact_text_container fade-in"><h1>contact</h1><h2>Torbj√∂rn Gustavsson</h2><p>torbjorn.gustavsson@klimator.se</p><p>+46 (0)709 170 252</p></div></div></div></section></body></html>